Number of listed shares (Common          : 1,200,000,000
Stock)(shares)
Number of paid-up Stocks  (Common        : 1,200,000,000
Stock)(shares)
Par value (baht per share)               : 0.25
Paid-up capital (baht)                   : 300,000,000.00
IPO shares (shares)                      : 300,000,000
IPO price (baht)                         : 3.35
Business description                     :
 COM7 distributes IT products such as laptops, desktop computers, mobile phones,
tablets, related accessories and product repair services. Moreover COM7 also
features services related to mobile phones such as opening a new phone number,
changing promotion package, changing mobile carrier, changing SIM card, and
requesting a new SIM card and bill payment service for utility bills, and
post-paid phone bills of AIS, DTAC, and TRUE. COM7 is the largest IT chain store
in term of branches. COM7 distributes IT products via its own branches which
are retail stores in leading department stores, shopping malls, and hypermarkets
covering Bangkok and upcountry provinces. The distribution channels can be
categorized into 3 channels: (1) Computers and computer-related products stores:
 Banana IT
(2) Apple stores, repair and service center of Apple products: iStudio by 
Comseven, iBeat by Comseven, U-Store by Comseven, and iCare
(3) Mobile phones and accessories stores: Banana Mobile, Samsung Shop
Remark                                   :
Please see the Information Memorandum of COM7 through PDF file.
